{"tid":533841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警向fb索印傭上載影片","createTime":"2018-01-19T08:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T14:12:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c3d6b318a2108278ba2e87887d3d2636b00c40","tid":533841,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180119/20279027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F20279027&d=Q2wpGJvAxivVVMlKozuYrf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=88217558\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F20279027&h=a7c5d19b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180119/20279027</a><br />\n<br />\n警向fb索印傭上載影片<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180119/large/a1302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180119%2Flarge%2Fa1302a.gif&h=03d70303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告昨續准保釋候訊。戴國輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【涉直播少主洗澡】<br />\n【本報訊】涉在社交媒體facebook直播僱主3名5至7歲子女洗澡的印傭，被控發佈兒童色情物品罪，案件昨在東區法院再訊。控方指印傭的手機找不到涉案洗澡裸體影片，亦找不到其他裸體影片，但印傭曾將影片上載至fb，警方已去信fb索取影片，現正等候對方回覆。<br />\n<br />\n由於控方需時繼續調查及諮詢律政司意見，故案件押後至3月1日再訊，被告Yuni Kristiani（28歲）續准保釋候訊。被告被控於去年12月1日在北角城市花園一單位內，用手機發佈一段含有3名兒童的兒童色情物品到fb。她離開法庭時發現記者拍照，手按記者鏡頭稱：「唔好影我呀！」<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC3408/17<br />\n■記者戴國輝"},{"pid":"59115e2605b24d8009ea4d6d47104deaa59d7d2f","tid":533841,"uid":14365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:22:16.000Z","msg":"唔好影你？咁你又影d細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48ee78e637514803440f3c0d84efe4c42ba0b8a","tid":533841,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"你影啲小朋友沖涼就得<br />\n你而家著晒衫就唔影得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d6b9a321db2855abb93a00ac4fb737d78f98d5","tid":533841,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"所有父母都影過小朋友裸照，即係製作過兒童色情，拉哂全香港父母丫笨撚柒。"},{"pid":"2d6bbe37039a7ba6360bfc44c0a6211b2f1819b3","tid":533841,"uid":15905,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"睇錯 索印傭 而㩒入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c1c4fcede22a8bc0c683583c33eb3fc8e76959","tid":533841,"uid":26617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66d6b9a321db2855abb93a00ac4fb737d78f98d5","tid":533841,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"所有父母都影過小朋友裸照，即係製作過兒童色情，拉哂全香港父母丫笨撚柒。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"用撚咗腦未？上載呀"},{"pid":"0fe208411255f0b0939a9731d206e0f2377d19f9","tid":533841,"uid":15477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d6bbe37039a7ba6360bfc44c0a6211b2f1819b3","tid":533841,"uid":15905,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"睇錯 索印傭 而㩒入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:31:55.000Z","msg":"x2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc777d6eb7daac02905b47406abd6ad24f2dcb3","tid":533841,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80c1c4fcede22a8bc0c683583c33eb3fc8e76959","tid":533841,"uid":26617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66d6b9a321db2855abb93a00ac4fb737d78f98d5","tid":533841,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"所有父母都影過小朋友裸照，即係製作過兒童色情，拉哂全香港父母丫笨撚柒。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"用撚咗腦未？上載呀"},"cit